        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>When you visit our website or make a purchase, we may collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal details like name, email, phone number, and shipping address.</li>
                <li>Payment information securely processed via our payment partners.</li>
                <li>Browsing data including pages viewed, items added to cart, and preferences.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the information collected to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Process and fulfill your orders efficiently.</li>
                <li>Provide customer support and respond to inquiries.</li>
                <li>Send promotional emails only if you opt-in.</li>
                <li>Improve our website, products, and services based on user preferences.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            <p>We use cookies to enhance your shopping experience, remember preferences, and analyze website traffic.
                You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may be affected.</p>

            <h2>Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement robust security measures to protect your personal information, including encryption and
                secure servers. Only authorized personnel have access to sensitive data.</p>

            <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>We may share information with trusted service providers for payment processing, shipping, and marketing
                purposes. These providers are contractually bound to protect your data.</p>

            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
                <li>Opt-out of marketing communications at any time.</li>
                <li>Contact us for privacy-related questions at support@artisanessentials.com.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
            <p>We may update this privacy policy occasionally. Changes will be posted on this page with the last updated
                date for your reference.</p>
